      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;The concentration of high density is downtown where we&rsquo;re building a high-rapid bus project,&rdquo; called VIVA, he says, adding the provincial government also wants the Yonge subway line to extend north into Richmond Hill. &ldquo;However, we are waiting for the City of Toronto to deal with all of their other projects, including the Scarborough subway and the (downtown) relief line,&rdquo; he says. &lt;strong&gt;FULL PAGE &ndash; IMAGE TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
