      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;The people living there aren&rsquo;t coming from Toronto, they&rsquo;re coming from within the community,&rdquo; said Steve Upton, director of special projects at Tridel. &ldquo;The project sold out because the units are bigger than you&rsquo;d find in downtown Toronto. There was demand for larger product from empty-nesters.&rdquo; Heathwood Homes built Forest Hill on the Green, a 117-detached housing project nearby. &lt;strong&gt;HALF WIDTH &ndash; IMAGE TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
