      },
      {
        "content": "Bartender Sarah Good, an area resident for 13 years, says she&rsquo;s noticed a budding skyline to the south where all the condo development is occurring. She also says the neighbourhood is replete with services and community centres, but she hopes the added density won&rsquo;t strain them. &ldquo;As a resident it&rsquo;s good to have more residents come in,&rdquo; she said, &ldquo;but services like medical and mental health need to keep up. I&rsquo;m just curious if services and infrastructure are going to match the population growth.&rdquo; &lt;strong&gt;SIDEBAR &ndash; RELATED STORY TEST &ndash; NONE&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "17",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "That&rsquo;s a trick question. Even though the vehicles, those at the centre of one of the automotive industry&rsquo;s largest&nbsp;controversies in its history, were released for sale on April 12&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt;, they&rsquo;re already long gone. The 2.0-litre TDI-equipped vehicles had been quarantined in the wake of Dieselgate, the world-wide emissions cheating scandal that brought the German automotive giant to its knees. &lt;strong&gt;NO LAYOUT &ndash; PULL QUOTE TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "18",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "<p>TEXT Pullquote</p><div>SOURCE Pullquote</div>",
            "_id": "1",
            "shortcode_tag": "pn-pullquote",
            "type": "blockquote",
            "shortcode": "[pn-pullquote  text=\"TEXT Pullquote\" source =\"SOURCE Pullquote\" hide =\"\" featured=\"true\" /]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "no_layout",
        "_id": "19",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"no_layout\"][pn-pullquote text=\"TEXT Pullquote\" source=\"SOURCE Pullquote\" featured=\"true\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "Since the discovery that VW had been intentionally, deviously, futzing with the pollution control software on many of its&nbsp;diesel cars since 2009, North American owners spent more than&nbsp;a year in limbo, awaiting settlement options for their tainted vehicles. When they were finally announced, those settlements were generous; depending on the age and condition of their vehicle, owners could see compensation that amounted to either a fix plus a payment of between $5,100 to $8,000, or a buyback based on the value of the car pre-scandal, plus that payment.&lt;strong&gt; COLUMN &ndash; PULL QUOTE TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "20",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "<p>TEXT - Pullquote</p><div>SOURCE - Pullquote</div>",
            "_id": "1",
            "shortcode_tag": "pn-pullquote",
            "type": "blockquote",
            "shortcode": "[pn-pullquote  text=\"TEXT - Pullquote\" source =\"SOURCE - Pullquote\" hide =\"\" /]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "column",
        "_id": "21",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"column\"][pn-pullquote text=\"TEXT - Pullquote\" source=\"SOURCE - Pullquote\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "In the meantime, inventory already on dealer lots was frozen. With the announcement of an approved fix by the EPA in the U.S. (and accepted in Canada), those impounded cars were cleared for sale. It&rsquo;s a move a lot of people were betting on, and a local dealer told me the 43 cars he had in stock were gone in a couple of days. &lt;strong&gt;SIDEBAR &ndash;&nbsp;PULL QUOTE TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "22",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "<p>TEXT Pullquote</p><div>SOURCE Pullquote</div>",
            "_id": "1",
            "shortcode_tag": "pn-pullquote",
            "type": "blockquote",
            "shortcode": "[pn-pullquote  text=\"TEXT Pullquote\" source =\"SOURCE Pullquote\" hide =\"\" /]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "sidebar",
        "_id": "23",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"sidebar\"][pn-pullquote text=\"TEXT Pullquote\" source=\"SOURCE Pullquote\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;Most of those cars had deposits on them all this time,&rdquo; explained Sean McLaughlin, business manager at Roseland Motors Ltd. in Burlington, Ontario. &ldquo;Some may have been speculators, but most are loyal VW customers.&rdquo; The released cars came with a good wallop of incentives for buyers willing to head back into the diesel waters. Take the 2015 Passat TDI, for example. Dealers were authorized to give buyers 0 per cent financing for 60 months plus $7,500 finance cash, or up to $9,500 cash. If you bought one, I hope you worked the deal, hard. &lt;strong&gt;COLUMN &ndash; VERSUS:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "24",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "What if you had an affected car and have already taken&nbsp;the VW money and ran? Are you allowed to double dip? Indeed. They&rsquo;re two separate transactions, according to Thomas Tetzlaff, manager of public relations for Volkswagen Canada. McLaughlin agrees, again pointing out that most of those scarce-on-the-ground 2015s went to long-time customers. &lt;strong&gt;COLUMN &ndash; YOU TUBE:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "25",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "provider_name": "YouTube",
