        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The newly released cars already will have had the first of the two-phase fix done to them, a software reflashing that Volkswagen Canada says goes most of the way to correcting the emissions problem.",
        "_id": "29",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;The follow-up fix, that we anticipate being ready in about a year, will be a hardware one, installing things like a particulate filter with greater longevity,&rdquo; explained Tetzlaff. &lt;strong&gt;NO LAYOUT &nbsp;&ndash; DROP CAPS:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "30",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
