        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"no_layout\"][pn_dropcap]L[/pn_dropcap][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "Should you have been rushing to purchase one of these cars? Or be disappointed that you missed the lottery? That depends.",
        "_id": "32",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The Automobile Protection Association (APA) reminds you to keep in mind these vehicles are two years old, and in some cases more. They&rsquo;ve been stored in anticipation of the court rulings and, while they may look like new cars with zero kilometres on them, consumers should be aware there could be latent problems in the event they were not cared for properly. Tires can develop flat spots&nbsp;&ndash; those tires have also had their lifespan used up, even sitting&nbsp;&ndash; brake lines could become corroded, and they&rsquo;ve been subject to the outdoor elements. &lt;strong&gt;FULL PAGE &ndash; GALLERY TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "33",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "[snapgallery id=\"1094211\" immersive=\"true\" /]",
            "_id": "1",
            "paragraph": "wrap",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "full_page",
        "_id": "34",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"full_page\"]</p>\n<p>[snapgallery id=\"1094211\" immersive=\"true\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;The APA&rsquo;s position is that the settlement offer is a good one, and consumers are well served by taking advantage of it and moving into a new car of their choosing, or another VW gasoline engine,&rdquo; says John Raymond of the APA. Those consumers are falling into three categories: those who ditch their diesels for the cash, those who accept the &ldquo;sorry&rdquo; cash and get their cars fixed but keep them, and a few diehards who will not surrender their beloved TDIs at all. &lt;strong&gt;FULL WIDTH &ndash; GALLERY TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "35",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "[snapgallery id=\"1093665\" immersive=\"true\" /]",
            "_id": "1",
            "paragraph": "wrap",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "full_width",
        "_id": "36",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"full_width\"]</p>\n<p>[snapgallery id=\"1093665\" immersive=\"true\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "There&rsquo;s a reason for that. With the amendments, the performance of these cars will be affected in two ways. First is how they drive, and second is their fuel economy. Those cheats enabled VW to deliver that famous diesel torque and 1,000-kilometre range to a tank of fuel. The fixes will impact both of those things. The APA maintains, however, that if VW found a way to cheat, there&rsquo;s no reason they shouldn&rsquo;t be able to find a way to fix it. Just be prepared to compromise. &lt;strong&gt;HALF WIDTH &ndash; GALLERY TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "37",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "[snapgallery id=\"1095300\" immersive=\"true\" /]",
            "_id": "1",
            "paragraph": "wrap",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "half_width_right",
        "_id": "38",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"half_width_right\"]</p>\n<p>[snapgallery id=\"1095300\" immersive=\"true\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "I asked Tetzlaff what steps dealers have been taking to offset these concerns, and how much help the parent company has given them.",
        "_id": "39",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;First, remember that this was September of 2015 when sales were halted, so we were getting to the last of the inventory. Dealers have been storing them, but many cars, not just these ones, are stored for periods of time by dealers. We had them on a 30-day basis, which means dealers were compensated for monthly upkeep on all of those cars, doing battery checks and keeping them ready for sale.&rdquo; &lt;strong&gt;COLUMN &ndash; GALLERY TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "40",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "[snapgallery id=\"1093562\" immersive=\"true\" /]",
            "_id": "1",
            "paragraph": "wrap",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "column",
        "_id": "41",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"column\"]</p>\n<p>[snapgallery id=\"1093562\" immersive=\"true\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "The APA warns significant time has passed, but Tetzlaff says VW has created a pre-delivery inspection that will alleviate any concerns.",
        "_id": "42",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;The PDI checklist is exhaustive,&rdquo; he explains. &ldquo;Fluids, tires, rotors and extensive warranty. These cars are as good as anything you can buy that was made yesterday.&rdquo; He also notes there is a high degree of certainty that we have seen the last of diesel passenger vehicles from VW in this country. &lt;strong&gt;SIDEBAR &ndash; GALLERY TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "43",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "content": "[snapgallery id=\"1095159\" immersive=\"true\" /]",
            "_id": "1",
            "paragraph": "wrap",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "sidebar",
        "_id": "44",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"sidebar\"]</p>\n<p>[snapgallery id=\"1095159\" immersive=\"true\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "It may be the end of an era, but it&rsquo;s one that Volkswagen will forever be tied to.",
        "_id": "45",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Long one of the region&rsquo;s best showcases for varied, new and exciting musical artists in a perfect setting, the Vancouver Folk Music Festival celebrates 40 years this year. Beginning with a free Thursday night concert in the park &mdash; details TBA &mdash; the three day event promises nearly 60 artists from 18 countries, 10 states and eight provinces and territories. &lt;strong&gt;COLUMN &ndash; INFO BOX TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "46",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "column2_title": "COLUMN TITLE #2",
            "column3_title": "COLUMN TITLE #3",
            "title": "MAIN TITILE #1",
            "column1_content": "COLUMN CONTENT #1",
            "column3_content": "COLUMN CONTENT #3",
            "column1_title": "COLUMN TITLE #1",
