        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"column\"][pn_additonal_info_boxes main_title=\"MAIN TITILE #1\" column1_title=\"COLUMN TITLE #1\" column1_content=\"COLUMN CONTENT #1\" column2_title=\"COLUMN TITLE #2\" column2_content=\"COLUMN CONTENT #2\" column3_title=\"COLUMN TITLE #3\" column3_content=\"COLUMN CONTENT #3\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "If you are feeling the budget crunch this season for travel, this means getting around while hanging out in the park.",
        "_id": "48",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1711_onscreen\"></div>",
        "_id": "49",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Returning fan favourites include UK singer Billy Bragg with Joe Henry playing songs from the acclaimed Shine A Light: Field Recordings From the Great American Railroad, Lilith Fair-era artist Shawn Colvin, Kathleen Edwards and women&rsquo;s music progenitor Ferron and her All-Star Band. Those who crave the latest rising stars from across the globe can appreciate exciting acts ranging from Congo&rsquo;s Mbongwana Star to Columbia&rsquo;s cumbia-tronic Sidesteppers, Greenland&rsquo;s Nive Nielsen &amp;amp; The Deer People and multiple JUNO Award-winner Alpha Ya Ya Diallo. If good old time back porch picking is to your preference, True Blues with Corey Harris and Alvin Youngblood Heart, Tift Merritt and Jim Kweskin&rsquo;s jug band action are sure to entertain.&lt;strong&gt; SIDEBAR&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;- INFO BOX TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "50",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "column2_title": "column2_title",
            "column3_title": "column3_title",
            "title": "main_title",
            "column1_content": "column1_content",
            "column3_content": "column3_content",
            "column1_title": "column1_title",
            "column2_content": "column2_content",
            "shortcode_tag": "pn_additonal_info_boxes",
            "_id": "1",
            "type": "infobox",
            "shortcode": "[pn_additonal_info_boxes main_title=\"main_title\" column1_title=\"column1_title\" column1_content=\"column1_content\" column2_title=\"column2_title\" column2_content=\"column2_content\" column3_title=\"column3_title\" column3_content=\"column3_content\" /]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "sidebar",
        "_id": "51",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"sidebar\"][pn_additonal_info_boxes main_title=\"main_title\" column1_title=\"column1_title\" column1_content=\"column1_content\" column2_title=\"column2_title\" column2_content=\"column2_content\" column3_title=\"column3_title\" column3_content=\"column3_content\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "As always, the VFMF pursues its founding mission statement of presenting performers who reflect the politics and struggles which folk music plays such a roll in propelling into the public mind. Expect topical and passionate material from Australian Aboriginal singer Archie Roach, labour singer Si Kahn and &mdash; perhaps one of the most anticipated group tour in this year&rsquo;s roster &mdash;&nbsp;Native North America: A Selection Of Indigenous Trailblazers Featuring Duke Redbird, Willie Thrasher and Linda Saddleback, Willy Mitchell, Lloyd Cheechoo, and Gordon Dick Sr. Former B.C. resident Cris Derksen brings her unique &ldquo;orchestral Pow Wow&rdquo; music as well. &lt;strong&gt;FULL PAGE &ndash; TRADITIONAL VIDEO TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "52",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "shortcode_tag": "kaltura-widget",
            "origin_cms": "kaltura",
            "origin_id": "0_ix8ng0lk",
            "_id": "1",
            "type": "video",
            "shortcode": "[kaltura-widget entryid=\"0_ix8ng0lk\" autoplay=\"\" showplaylist=\"\" featured=\"\" playertype=\"video\" ]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "full_page",
        "_id": "53",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"full_page\"][kaltura-widget entryid=\"0_ix8ng0lk\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "That&rsquo;s just a smattering of the roster.",
        "_id": "54",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Plus, don&rsquo;t think Canada isn&rsquo;t well represented. Such CBC regulars as John K. Samson and the Winter Wheat (Manitoba), Jim Bryson (Ontario) and Hillsburn (Nova Scotia) join B.C.&rsquo;s C.R. Avery, The Belle Game and the legendary Roy Forbes through the weekend. &nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;FULL WIDTH &ndash; TRADITIONAL VIDEO TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "55",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "shortcode_tag": "kaltura-widget",
            "origin_cms": "kaltura",
            "origin_id": "0_s1oabr4w",
            "_id": "1",
            "type": "video",
            "shortcode": "[kaltura-widget entryid=\"0_s1oabr4w\" autoplay=\"\" showplaylist=\"\" featured=\"\" playertype=\"video\" ]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "full_width",
        "_id": "56",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"full_width\"][kaltura-widget entryid=\"0_s1oabr4w\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "Author and Internet star Lilly Singh&rsquo;s book tour for&nbsp;&lt;a href=&rdquo;http://lillysinghbook.com/&rdquo;&gt;How to be a Bawse&lt;/a&gt; is like a military operation.",
        "_id": "57",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "No fan will be left behind.",
        "_id": "58",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;I&rsquo;m meeting everyone; I met 680 people at the venue yesterday (Tuesday),&rdquo; said the Scarborough, Ont., native who now calls Los Angeles home. &lt;strong&gt;HALF&nbsp;WIDTH &ndash; TRADITIONAL VIDEO TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "59",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "shortcode_tag": "kaltura-widget",
            "origin_cms": "kaltura",
            "origin_id": "1_5t193irh",
            "_id": "1",
            "type": "video",
            "shortcode": "[kaltura-widget entryid=\"1_5t193irh\" autoplay=\"\" showplaylist=\"\" featured=\"\" playertype=\"video\" ]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "half_width_right",
        "_id": "60",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"half_width_right\"][kaltura-widget entryid=\"1_5t193irh\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "That sold-out venue was in Vancouver, the midway point in a 12-country, 34-stop tour that also had her in Burnaby April 26.",
        "_id": "61",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Singh, a.k.a. Superwoman, who has &lt;a href=&rdquo;https://www.youtube.com/user/IISuperwomanII&rdquo; target=&rdquo;_blank&rdquo;&gt;11.5 million YouTube subscribers&lt;/a&gt; and over one billion views, is now firmly in the land of real live traditional media with her new book. &lt;strong&gt;COLUMN &ndash; TRADITIONAL VIDEO TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "62",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "shortcode_tag": "kaltura-widget",
            "origin_cms": "kaltura",
            "origin_id": "1_5t193irh",
            "_id": "1",
            "type": "video",
            "shortcode": "[kaltura-widget entryid=\"1_5t193irh\" autoplay=\"\" showplaylist=\"\" featured=\"\" playertype=\"video\" ]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "column",
        "_id": "63",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"column\"][kaltura-widget entryid=\"1_5t193irh\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1711_onscreen\"></div>",
        "_id": "64",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Subtitled A Guide to Conquering Life, it&nbsp;is&nbsp;a self-help book that encourages readers to follow their dreams and get the job done, Singh-style. That style is simple: work hard.&lt;strong&gt; SIDEBAR &ndash; TRADITIONAL VIDEO TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "65",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "shortcode_tag": "kaltura-widget",
            "origin_cms": "kaltura",
            "origin_id": "0_s1oabr4w",
            "_id": "1",
            "type": "video",
            "shortcode": "[kaltura-widget entryid=\"0_s1oabr4w\" autoplay=\"\" showplaylist=\"\" featured=\"\" playertype=\"video\" ]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "sidebar",
        "_id": "66",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"sidebar\"][kaltura-widget entryid=\"0_s1oabr4w\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;It&rsquo;s been a little more strenuous in that sense,&rdquo; said Singh about the meet-and-greet aspect of the tour. &ldquo;It&rsquo;s manageable. I hope and think.",
        "_id": "67",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;It&rsquo;s actually smaller than my last tour in terms of the production. My last tour was theatrical dancers. The show is actually less intense,&rdquo; added the 28-year-old, who was on Forbes&rsquo;s.&lt;strong&gt; FULL PAGE &ndash; IMMERSIVE VIDEO TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "68",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "channels": [
          "phone",
          "desktop",
          "tablet"
        ],
        "content_object": [
          {
            "origin_id": "0_ix8ng0lk",
            "display": "immersive",
            "shortcode_tag": "pn_featured_video_embed",
            "origin_cms": "kaltura",
            "description": "Testing....",
            "thumbnail": "Thumbnail ..",
            "_id": "1",
            "type": "video",
            "shortcode": "[pn_featured_video_embed entryid=\"0_ix8ng0lk\" autoplay=\"true\"]"
          }
        ],
        "shortcode_tag": "pn_embed",
        "location": "full_page",
        "_id": "69",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"full_page\"][pn_featured_video_embed entryid=\"0_ix8ng0lk\" description=\"Testing....\" thumbnail=\"Thumbnail ..\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;The flow is everything. The flow is the make or break with me. I&rsquo;m very particular as to who is positioned where, and who does what. For safety and to make sure everyone has the best time possible,&rdquo; said Singh, whose YouTube videos include guest stars like Michelle Obama, The Rock and, most recently, Bill Gates. &lt;strong&gt;FULL WIDTH &ndash; IMMERSIVE VIDEO TEST:&lt;/strong&gt;",
        "_id": "70",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
