        "_id": "71",
        "type": "wrapper",
        "shortcode": "[wrapper mobile=\"show\" desktop=\"show\" location=\"full_width\"][pn_featured_video_embed entryid=\"0_ix8ng0lk\" description=\"Description.....\" thumbnail=\"??????????????\" /][/wrapper]"
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;It&rsquo;s very much down to a science. I have it broken down to how everyone can have the best time.&rdquo;",
