      {
        "content": "<div class=\"story-content\"> <div id=\"page1\"> <div> <p><img id=\"storyphoto\" class=\"wp-post-image\" title=\"Penn at the Snowden premiere recently, pre-Leila George.\" src=\"http://www.ottawacitizen.com/entertainment/cms/binary/12261509.jpg?size=sw620x65\" alt=\"Sean Penn, 56, hits red carpet with new girlfriend, Vincent DâOnofrioâs daughter, Leila George, 24\"></p> <p>Sean Penn has a new lady in his life, in the form of Leila George, Law &amp; Order actor Vincent DâOnofrioâs 24-year-old daughter, confirms <a href=\"http://people.com/movies/sean-penn-is-dating-law-order-star-vincent-donofrios-daughter-leila-george/\" target=\"_blank\">People</a>.</p> <p>The pair were spotted in Hawaii on Wednesday, frolicking in the ocean.</p> <div class=\"embed\"> <div class=\"embed-twitter\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-error\"> <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Sean Penn spotted kissing Law &amp; Order star Vincent D’Onofrio’s daughter, Leila George <a href=\"https://t.co/MvNhGfoxG5\">https://t.co/MvNhGfoxG5</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/P7Z1dScJmW\">pic.twitter.com/P7Z1dScJmW</a></p> <p>â People Magazine (@people) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/people/status/784368482578202624\">October 7, 2016Â Â  </a></p>\n</blockquote> </div> </div> <p>TheyÂ thenÂ stepped out on Thursday together on the red carpet forÂ the Film Independent LACMA event, An Evening with Sean Penn, in Los Angeles.</p> <p>George also shared an Instagram shot of the two in a recording studio together recently.</p> <p>Penn, 56, previously dated Charlize Theron, but the two split in June 2015. Before then, he was married to Robin Wright from 1996 to 2010, and Madonna from 1985 to 1989.</p> <div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1715\" class=\" fsk_splitbox_1715\"></div> <p>He has two children with Wright: daughter Dylan, 25, and son Hopper, 23, meaning George is a mere year younger than his daughter.</p> <p class=\"p1\">George, born to DâOnofrio and his then-girlfriend Greta Scacchi, recently appeared in Mother, May I Sleep with Danger, co-starring James Franco.</p> </div> </div> </div>",
