        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;You&acirc;re playing better, so you feel better,&rdquo; MacLean says. &ldquo;Everything&acirc;s looser and you&acirc;re not quite as tight and tentative as you were before you started to have success.&rdquo;",
