          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "After posting victories over the Boston Bruins and Washington Capitals, the Senators are currently riding a two-game winning streak and have an opportunity to match their season-high three-game winning streak set that occurred from November 5",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "open",
