    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/business/local-business/a-cup-of-strawberries-a-day-regulates-blood-sugar-quebec-study/wcm/daf4df8a-c10f-468e-9474-1db372aea271",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "A cup of strawberries a day regulates blood sugar: Quebec study"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "title": "Image title",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ],
        "_id": "1",
        "url": "http://www.ottawacitizen.com/health/cms/binary/12125131.jpg?size=sw620x65",
        "type": "image"
      },
      {
        "content": "Daily consumption of about one cup of strawberries can reportedly&Acirc;&nbsp;help regulate the blood sugar of people with Type 2 diabetes.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "These are the findings of a study presented at the International Strawberry Symposium, which will run until&Acirc;&nbsp;Wednesday at the Quebec City Convention Centre.",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The clinical study, led by Yves Desjardins, professor of horticulture at Universit&Atilde;&copy; Laval, was conducted on 50 people who were mildly obese and suffered from early Type 2 diabetes.",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;When they consumed about 250 grams of strawberries a day, we could reduce a very very important glucose intolerance and improve insulin sensitivity,&acirc; said Desjardins, who also serves as co-president of the symposium.",
        "_id": "5",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The research demonstrated that the ingestion of a serving of strawberries has a similar effect on patients as metformin, a drug commonly used to treat patients with Type 2 diabetes",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1715\" class=\" fsk_splitbox_1715\"></div>",
        "_id": "7",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;Our results are almost equivalent to a pharmaceutical treatment,&acirc; said Desjardins. &acirc;Just by eating strawberries and other berries, you can almost regulate blood sugar.&acirc;",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The health benefits of strawberries on mainly due to their polyphenols, compounds that reduce the incidence of certain metabolic diseases.",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "During the five-day meeting, several other scientific advances will be presented to about&Acirc;&nbsp;600 researchers and producers from 30 countries who are meeting in Quebec.",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Studies notably being presented to the public will focus on the consumption of&Acirc;&nbsp;strawberries for preventing cognitive decline, combatting skin cancer and reducing obesity.",
        "_id": "11",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The large international conference meets the world&acirc;s experts every four years.&Acirc;&nbsp;The event, now in its eighth year, is taking place in Canada for the first time.",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;This is the Strawberry Olympics,&acirc; Desjardins said.",
        "_id": "13",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Researchers will also present new varieties of strawberries becoming available on shelves in coming years, as well as more efficient production methods.",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
