    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/entertainment/local-arts/sexual-perfume-the-many-scents-of-desire/wcm/ea553ad4-ea44-469c-a403-9c53d0c721f1",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "Sexual perfume: The many scents of desire"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "title": "Image title",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ],
        "_id": "1",
        "url": "http://wpmedia.ottawacitizen.com/2016/05/img_0042.jpg?quality=55&strip=all&w=840&h=630&crop=1",
        "type": "image"
      },
      {
        "content": "With a catchy name like S&Atilde;&copy;xual and an irresistible storyline, Michel Germain created a splashy entrance on the fragrance scene 20 years ago.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "With more than 25 perfumes to his name, the master marketer from Almonte has managed to hold his own in the competitive and fickle world of fragrance.",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&nbsp;",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<figure class=\"wp-caption post-img size_this_image_test align-center\" id=\"attachment_818943\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text wp-caption\"><span class=\"img-caption\">The Sexual Paris collection glass bottles for men and women feature a slight indent in the centre to represent a personâs midriff. âBoth of these scents sit nicely on the skin,â says Michel Germain. âThe shapes of the bottles are very organic. Your thumb goes right into the centre of the bottle, which is a subliminal thing that resembles a womanâs midriff.â He added that there are 180 hand-glued pink crystals on the womenâs fragrance bottle, while the menâs bottle is a masculine silver and midnight blue bottle.</span> <span class=\"img-author\">BRUNO SCHLUMBERGER / OTTAWA CITIZEN STYLE</span></figcaption></figure>",
        "_id": "5",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "He credits his success to creating a strong brand identity, developing pleasing scents and his loyal retailers &acirc; Hudson&acirc;s Bay and Bloomingdale&acirc;s, a chain of luxury department stores owned by Macy&acirc;s in the United States.",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;In fall 1994, I launched in four Hudson&acirc;s Bay stores. Now, we&acirc;re in full distribution in 90 stores. It&acirc;s very important to pick and chose your allies,&acirc; Germain says.",
        "_id": "7",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&nbsp;",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&Atilde;&copy;xual Paris, a romantic fragrance and beauty care collection for men and women, is his latest creation, which features perfume, eau de toilette, rollerballs, lotions and deodorant.",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;Paris conjures up images of romance. The name makes a strong expression and has a special meaning. It&acirc;s romantic and sophisticated.&acirc;",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "While Germain travels often to Toronto and New York, the father of three sons remains humble by his success. He and his wife, Norma Germain, run their company from their 100-acre rural property near Almonte, while their main manufacturing and distribution centre is in Carleton Place.",
        "_id": "11",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&nbsp;",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;It really doesn&acirc;t matter where you live when you have a BlackBerry or laptop. We&acirc;ve got the best of both worlds,&acirc; says Germain, who has planted more 3,000 trees on his property.",
        "_id": "13",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The couple, married 26 years, created enormous buzz after Germain said S&Atilde;&copy;xual was inspired by his love for his wife, who desired a scent to feel sexy. The former engineering technologist spent several years experimenting with alluring ingredients after Norma mentioned she couldn&acirc;t find a fragrance she liked. They continue to work with New York&acirc;s International Flavors and Fragrances Inc., the world&acirc;s largest perfume-oil company, to produce their scents.",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Norma, the wordsmith in the family, writes most of the material for the company.",
        "_id": "15",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&nbsp;",
        "_id": "16",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;The digital world is the new reality. It&acirc;s a changing world and you have to stay relevant or you die. We write in sentences rather than in paragraphs and are moving to video to create visuals,&acirc; she says.",
        "_id": "17",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The couple is proud of their achievement and enjoy their lifestyle.",
        "_id": "18",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;Looking back over the past 20 years we&acirc;re very pleased with our accomplishments. We have a nice home, strong reputation and have managed to employ a whole bunch of people,&acirc; says Germain.",
        "_id": "19",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;We feel good about the next 10 years. It&acirc;s a world market now and you need to have a world vision.&acirc;",
        "_id": "20",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&nbsp;",
        "_id": "21",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
