    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/entertainment/local-arts/victorias-secret-is-in-hot-water-over-alleged-photoshopping-of-models-martha-hunt-stella-maxwell/wcm/384b297b-946e-4ba0-a09a-de5ff400a3fd",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "Victoria’s Secret is in hot water over alleged Photoshopping of models Martha Hunt, Stella Maxwell"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "title": "Image title",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ],
        "_id": "1",
        "url": "http://www.ottawacitizen.com/entertainment/cms/binary/12114326.jpg?size=sw620x65",
        "type": "image"
      },
      {
        "content": "Last week, Victoria&acirc;s Secret posted an Instagram&Acirc;&nbsp;photo of Martha Hunt and Stella Maxwell wearing Body by Victoria bras, but something about the ad doesn&acirc;t seem to sit well with its followers.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "To models Hunt and&Acirc;&nbsp;Maxwell, it&acirc;s just another day in the fashion industry, but for the public, it&acirc;s yet another overzealous airbrushing job that reinforces unrealistic beauty standards.",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Hunt&Acirc;&nbsp;has become a&Acirc;&nbsp;topic of discussion around the spheres of social media, with commenters noting that the white patches around her&Acirc;&nbsp;arm don&acirc;t quite blend into the background of the photo, and that her torso appears to be fading directly into the grey backdrop. What&acirc;s also puzzling is that her&Acirc;&nbsp;left arm seems unusually long, as it appears to be reaching all the way over to the other side of Maxwell.",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "It has not been confirmed whether Photoshop was actually used in the photo, as Victoria&acirc;s Secret has yet to comment on the ad. But the lingerie powerhouse is no stranger to this kind of public backlash. ",
        "_id": "5",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2015/10/08/victorias-secret-accused-of-photoshopping-out-models-butt-cheek-5428370/\" target=\"_blank\">Last year</a>",
        "_id": "6",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": ", they were called out online for completely Photoshopping out a model&acirc;s butt cheek, while a t-shirt model appeared to lose&Acirc;&nbsp;one of her arms.",
        "_id": "7",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Photoshop and airbrushing is a part of the industry, but what social media users seem to be&Acirc;&nbsp;calling for is some discretion for maintaining the basic human form.",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      }
