    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/entertainment/local-arts/it-was-totally-his-fault-there-is-no-one-else-to-blame-heath-ledgers-father-reflects-on-his-sons-fatal-overdose/wcm/f4168d10-2418-4312-88df-11c60b0049b3",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "‘It was totally his fault, there is no one else to blame’: Heath Ledger’s father reflects on his son’s fatal overdose"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "content": "It&acirc;s been almost a decade since actor Heath Ledger died in January 2008 at the age of 28 after mixing sleeping pills and painkillers, but his family continues to mourn their loss.",
        "_id": "1",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Recalling his&Acirc;&nbsp;accidental overdose, father Kim Ledger is using the experience for good, working towards raising awareness&Acirc;&nbsp;for the addictive opioid painkillers that contributed to&Acirc;&nbsp;his son&acirc;s death.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;It was totally his fault, there is no one else to blame,&acirc; Kim said in an interview with the ",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3708126/Heath-Ledger-s-father-Kim-painfully-recalls-actor-s-accidental-overdose-speaks-against-addictive-opioid-painkillers-killed-son.html\" target=\"_blank\">Daily Mail Australia</a>",
        "_id": "4",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": ".",
        "_id": "5",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "In the final hours of his son&acirc;s life, he said that he and his daughter Kate warned Ledger against opioid tablets, in an attempt&Acirc;&nbsp;to prevent the ongoing addiction.",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Kim,&Acirc;&nbsp;66, a businessman from Perth, now leads a non-profit organization called ScriptWise. Backed by the Ledger family, the research carried out by the organization aims to raise awareness&Acirc;&nbsp;for &acirc;the safe and appropriate use of prescription medications,&acirc; focusing specifically on &acirc;medications most susceptible to misuse such as opioid analgesics and benzodiazepines,&acirc; the Scriptwise website says.",
        "_id": "7",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1715\" class=\" fsk_splitbox_1715\"></div>",
        "_id": "8",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Kim alleged in the interview that the doctors Ledger went to&Acirc;&nbsp;might have played a role in the actor&acirc;s death.",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;In the case of someone with a higher profile, it&acirc;s often a case of &acirc;what do you want&acirc; instead of &acirc;what do you need,&rsquo;&acirc; Kim said.",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;There&acirc;s so much pressure on them to perform so even though your body is telling you that it&acirc;s not good and needs time, it&acirc;s like &acirc;just take these painkillers and keep going.&rsquo;&acirc;",
        "_id": "11",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Late in February 2008, a federal investigation into Ledger&acirc;s death exonerated two American physicians&Acirc;&nbsp;of any wrongdoing, citing that&Acirc;&nbsp;the doctors in question had prescribed the actor&Acirc;&nbsp;other medications&Acirc;&nbsp;than the ones that killed him.",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Mary-Kate Olsen was named in a later investigation, but was cleared of any wrongdoing, as Ledger had reportedly phoned&Acirc;&nbsp;her before making an emergency 911 call on the day of his death. &Acirc;&nbsp;The two were friends at the time,&Acirc;&nbsp;and were rumoured to be dating.",
        "_id": "13",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "With the clearing of the two doctors and Olsen, and the closing of the investigation, it is still not known how Ledger obtained the oxycodone and hydrocodone that ultimately lead to his death.",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      }
