    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/entertainment/celebrity/doug-camilli-mtv-awards-snub-is-the-tide-turning-on-taylor-swift/wcm/acdb1b9f-bbae-4c29-85cf-d39734a3289c",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "Doug Camilli: MTV awards snub: Is the tide turning on Taylor Swift?"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "title": "Image title",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ],
        "_id": "1",
        "url": "http://www.ottawacitizen.com/entertainment/cms/binary/11857501.jpg?size=sw620x65",
        "type": "image"
      },
      {
        "content": "<strong>Did we just pass</strong>",
        "_id": "2",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " Peak Swift?",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Taylor Swift has probably had to expand some of ",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://www.glamour.com/story/taylor-swift-homes-celebrity-real-estate\" target=\"_blank\">her numerous homes</a>",
        "_id": "5",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " to accommodate all the trophies, statuettes, plaques and prizes she has collected over the years. From Academy of Country Music Awards to YouTube Music Awards, she&acirc;s got more hardware than Home Depot.",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "But this week, following her messy Calvin Harris breakup and that squabble with Kanye West, Swift was utterly passed over for MTV&acirc;s Video Music Awards &acirc; not a single nomination. Last year she had 10, winning four.",
        "_id": "7",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Swift&acirc;s been heard to worry, sometimes, about over-exposure; we may finally be there. New York mag even published a piece entitled When Did the Media Turn Against Taylor Swift? Is this the beginning of the end?",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "***",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1715\" class=\" fsk_splitbox_1715\"></div>",
        "_id": "10",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<strong>Jared Leto tells</strong>",
        "_id": "11",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " Rolling Stone about&Acirc;&nbsp;",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "none",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/features/jared-leto-the-unlikely-triumphs-of-a-rock-star-movie-star-w430833\" target=\"_blank\">his teenage hobby</a>",
        "_id": "13",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": ": &acirc;My experience with drugs? I did them, lots of them. A lot of them were really fun.&acirc;",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "But &acirc;&acirc;&brvbar; at some point, too, there&acirc;s a decision: &acirc;Is this going to be my life?&acirc; I made a choice to pursue other dreams. I guess that&acirc;s just the kind of (bad word) thing about a lot of drugs: The opportunity cost is too high. Some drugs are incredible, but the risk versus reward is out of line.&acirc;",
        "_id": "15",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "He&acirc;s 44.",
        "_id": "16",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "***",
        "_id": "17",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<strong>The astonishing Claudia</strong>",
        "_id": "18",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " Schiffer is embroiled in a nasty controversy in Majorca, where her gardener allegedly cut down two pine trees blocking the view from her mansion. Unfortunately, these ",
        "_id": "19",
        "paragraph": "none",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://www.express.co.uk/celebrity-news/694134/Claudia-Schiffer-gardener-broke-into-neighbours-home-cut-down-tree\" target=\"_blank\">trees were on somebody elseâs property,</a>",
        "_id": "20",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&Acirc;&nbsp;the Daily Express reports.",
        "_id": "21",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "And not just any &acirc;somebody else.&acirc; Willi Weber, former manager for Formula 1 driver Michael Schumacher, has lodged a criminal complaint, alleging that the former top model ordered the gardener to wield his saw.",
        "_id": "22",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "This all happened in Andratx, a swanky municipality at the southwest tip of Majorca, a Spanish island in the Mediterranean. The case has been dragging on for a year, the Daily Express reports, but now Claudia and hubby Matthew Vaughn may find themselves in court, the local paper Diario de Mallorca reports. The gardener has already been questioned.",
        "_id": "23",
