    "titles": {
      "main": "If a fitness promise seems too good to be true, it is"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "title": "Image title",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ],
        "_id": "1",
        "url": "http://www.ottawacitizen.com/health/cms/binary/12125830.jpg?size=sw620x65",
        "type": "image"
      },
      {
        "content": "If you believe late-night television, the elixir of healthy living ends in a 99.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>For 10 easy payments of $29.99, you can sport ripped abs, curvy hips and shapely thighs.Â </em>",
        "_id": "3",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>Why spend hours in the gym grunting and sweating when, for only five minutes a day, unwanted pounds can melt like butter as you tighten and shape muscle.Â </em>",
        "_id": "4",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>The Core Maker 2000 is revolutionizing the fitness world! Itâs affordable, effective and conveniently stores under your bed â where it will stay until you move out or upgrade your shag carpet.</em>",
        "_id": "5",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>Our crack research team has uncovered countless life-changing case studies and talked to many doctors.</em>",
        "_id": "6",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>My name is Doctor Schyster and I endorse this product.</em>",
        "_id": "7",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>Note: Results may vary. In addition to using the CM2000, case study subjects dramatically reduced calorie intake and enrolled in an intensive six month weight training regime. Doctor Schyster is not a medical doctor â his first name was legally changed to Doctor.</em>",
        "_id": "8",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1715\" class=\" fsk_splitbox_1715\"></div>",
        "_id": "9",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Let&acirc;s set a couple things straight.",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "First, those muscular fitness models in the commercial didn&acirc;t use the product to get where they are &acirc; maybe financially, but not physically. Chances are, the only time they ever got on the thing was during the taping of the commercial.",
        "_id": "11",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Second, the top medical schools have been strangely absent from late-night television. For some reason they&acirc;ve passed the baton of health education to former sitcom actors who have been charged with communicating groundbreaking weight-loss breakthroughs.",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "With all of the miracle cures and quick fixes out there, it&acirc;s hard to know which way to turn.",
        "_id": "13",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "I was amused at a recent trade show by the fast-talking salesperson promising amazing results by sitting on a vibrating platform. I was saddened to see the crowd reaching for their wallets to purchase this very expensive doorstop.",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Before you pull out your credit card and dial 1-800, measure every too-good-to-be-true promise against the following tips. Anything that claims otherwise is focused on your bank account, not your health.",
        "_id": "15",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Who knows, maybe you ",
        "_id": "16",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>can</em>",
        "_id": "17",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " achieve big results with minimal effort. Hey, maybe I can become fluent in Spanish in only five minutes a day. ",
        "_id": "18",
        "paragraph": "none",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<em>Lo dudo mucho!</em>",
        "_id": "19",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "For those who missed the point, the CM2000 isn&acirc;t a real product. Please don&acirc;t send me your credit card numbers. It doesn&acirc;t deflate your stomach &acirc; only your bank account.",
