    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/news/local-news/double-billed-funeral-due-to-record-confusion-says-hulse-playfair-mcgarry/wcm/30845f95-382d-405c-a347-6b48b9820379",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "Double billed funeral due to record 'confusion,' says Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "content": "When Sarah Harrison&Acirc;&nbsp;received a bill for nearly $6,000 from ",
        "_id": "1",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://ottawacitizen.com/tag/hulse-playfair-mcgarry\" target=\"_blank\">Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry</a>",
        "_id": "2",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " after&Acirc;&nbsp;her 94-year-old grandmother&acirc;s death in April, she was taken aback.&Acirc;&nbsp;&acirc;I thought, &acirc;Wait a second, I already paid for all this.&acirc;&Acirc;&nbsp; &acirc;",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Harrison had prepaid the funeral for her grandmother, Sheila Wren, at the prominent Ottawa company&acirc;s chapel at 150 Woodroffe Ave. in 2011. But when Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry said it&Acirc;&nbsp;had no record of the payment, she began&Acirc;&nbsp;to doubt herself.",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;I thought maybe I&acirc;d arranged it, but I hadn&acirc;t paid,&acirc; she said. &acirc;I was going through boxes, trying to find cancelled cheques.&acirc;",
        "_id": "5",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Fortunately Harrison, who runs her own business in Melancthon, Ont., north of Orangeville, is a very organized person. She was able to locate a copy of the pre-arrangements and email it&Acirc;&nbsp;to the company.",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Three days later, Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry sent her an adjusted invoice for $843.25, which included a $495 fee for &acirc;cemetery equipment and set up&acirc; &acirc;&Acirc;&nbsp;a&Acirc;&nbsp;service she also thought she&acirc;d&Acirc;&nbsp;paid for in 2011. At the company&acirc;s request, Harrison emailed a copy of that documentation, as well.",
        "_id": "7",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_1715\" class=\" fsk_splitbox_1715\"></div>",
        "_id": "8",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Her&Acirc;&nbsp;troubles weren&acirc;t over yet. She received two more erroneous invoices, including one dated May 9 for $559.35 that still&Acirc;&nbsp;listed&Acirc;&nbsp;the pre-paid charge for cemetery equipment and set up.",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;Even when they agreed that I&acirc;d already paid an amount,&acirc; Harrison said, &acirc;they still sent me a bill for it again. I literally had to go back to them three times to get the bill settled.",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;I felt like I was banging my head against a wall, trying to sort it out.&acirc;",
        "_id": "11",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "It wasn&acirc;t until May 30 &acirc; four weeks after her grandmother&acirc;s funeral &acirc; that Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry sent her an invoice showing the funeral was paid in full.",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<figure class=\"wp-caption post-img size_this_image_test aligncenter\" id=\"attachment_862682\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-862682\" src=\"http://wpmedia.ottawacitizen.com/2016/08/a-young-sheila-wren-sarah-harrisons-grandmother-wren-died.jpeg?quality=55&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"A young Sheila Wren, Sarah Harrison's grandmother. Wren died in Ottawa in April at age 94.\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text wp-caption\"><span class=\"img-caption\">A young Sheila Wren, Sarah Harrisonâs grandmother. Wren died in Ottawa in April at age 94.</span> <span class=\"img-author\">. / PHOTO SUPPLIED</span></figcaption></figure>",
        "_id": "13",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Harrison was so upset that she filed a formal complaint in July with the ",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://www.bereavementauthorityontario.ca/\" target=\"_blank\">Bereavement Authority of Ontario</a>",
        "_id": "15",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": ",&Acirc;&nbsp;an industry-funded, not-for-profit&Acirc;&nbsp;corporation that administers provisions and associated regulations of the Funeral, Burial and Cremation Services Act&Acirc;&nbsp;on behalf of the Ontario government. A BAO inspector subsequently contacted Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry for an explanation.",
        "_id": "16",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "In her complaint, Harrison&Acirc;&nbsp;expressed &acirc;serious concerns that if this happened to me, it could well have happened to other customers.",
        "_id": "17",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;People don&acirc;t think clearly when they are bereaved,&acirc; she wrote. &acirc;It seems ridiculous to be spelling this out, but a funeral home must keep accurate financial records.&acirc;",
        "_id": "18",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "She&Acirc;&nbsp;said her cousin, the other executor on her grandmother&acirc;s estate, told her he would have assumed the bill was accurate and paid it in full had it been sent to him.",
        "_id": "19",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "On Friday, Patrick McGarry, who co-owns the company with Sharon McGarry, explained the &acirc;confusion&acirc;&Acirc;&nbsp;in a letter to the Citizen.",
        "_id": "20",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div><a href=\"http://www.scribd.com/doc/321026136\">View this document on Scribd</a></div>",
        "_id": "21",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "He said the &acirc;most significant contributing factor&acirc; was that the prepaid funeral arrangement was not with Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry, but with McGarry Memorial Funeral Home, a separate company in Wakefield, which has its own files and independent operation.",
        "_id": "22",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The Wakefield company is&Acirc;&nbsp;owned by the Brian McGarry Family Trust, controlled by Sharon McGarry and her ex-husband Brian McGarry, who was ",
        "_id": "23",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/brian-mcgarry-dismissed-by-hulse-playfair-mcgarry\" target=\"_blank\">fired</a>",
        "_id": "24",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " by&Acirc;&nbsp;Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry in 2014,&Acirc;&nbsp;sparking&Acirc;&nbsp;a",
        "_id": "25",
        "paragraph": "none",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/court-battle-looms-between-brian-mcgarry-and-firm-over-disclosure-of-recordings\" target=\"_blank\">legal battle</a>",
        "_id": "26",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " between the firm&Acirc;&nbsp;and its one-time chief executive and public face.",
        "_id": "27",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Initially, the funeral director at Hulse, Playfair &amp; McGarry was unable to locate any record of the prepaid funeral arrangement, leading him to bill Harrison for the full amount, Patrick McGarry said.",
        "_id": "28",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Complicating matters further was that the contract showed some items, including a fee for cemetery equipment, that had not been prepaid, he&Acirc;&nbsp;said. Despite that, &acirc;we discovered that it had in fact been included in the original quote.",
        "_id": "29",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<figure class=\"wp-caption post-img size_this_image_test aligncenter\" id=\"attachment_862683\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-862683\" src=\"http://wpmedia.ottawacitizen.com/2016/08/the-aged-hands-of-sheila-wren-in-the-hands-of-her-granddaug.jpeg?quality=55&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"The aged hands of Sheila Wren in the hands of her granddaughter, Sarah Harrison. Wren died in Ottawa in April at age 94.\"></figure>",
        "_id": "30",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"img-caption\">The aged hands of Sheila Wren in the hands of her granddaughter, Sarah Harrison. Wren died in Ottawa in April at age 94.</span>",
        "_id": "31",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"img-author\">. / PHOTO SUPPLIED</span>",
        "_id": "32",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;Unfortunately, due to an inadvertent error, that item had failed to be reflected on the final prepaid contract. When it was pointed out to us, the director removed the cost as a good faith measure.&acirc;",
        "_id": "33",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "When Harrison&acirc;s complaint reached his desk, McGarry said he reviewed everything closely. &acirc;I wanted to make sure that we did everything we could to make it right.&acirc;",
        "_id": "34",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The company also provided additional services worth more than $1,000 at no cost to the family, he said.&Acirc;&nbsp;&acirc;Although rare in occurrence, when a problem or issue arises, our approach is to quickly and directly resolve it.&acirc;",
        "_id": "35",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "He said the funeral firm has &acirc;reviewed and refined&acirc; its processes to prevent similar errors in the future, &acirc;including updating our software program to close any gap in information.&acirc;",
        "_id": "36",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "McGarry&Acirc;&nbsp;spoke to Harrison by phone Friday. &acirc;I was finally able to explain to her the full situation and to apologize for the extra stresses that the billing issue created.&acirc;",
        "_id": "37",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "In light of McGarry&acirc;s explanation, Michael D&acirc;Mello, the BAO&acirc;s manager of licensing, said he saw no need to continue the investigation into the complaint.",
        "_id": "38",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "After speaking to McGarry, Harrison said she was still struggling.&Acirc;&nbsp;",
        "_id": "39",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"s1\">âHe was very apologetic and described a series of unfortunate errors with no ill intent, and said if a prepaid funeral was paid for again, in error, the double payment would have been caught and corrected at year end,â she said.</span>",
        "_id": "40",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"s1\">âOn the other hand, I am still notÂ convinced that this couldnât have, or hasnât, happened to someone else.â</span>",
        "_id": "41",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      }
    ],
