      },
      {
        "content": "<strong>WAKING THE SLEEPING CAIMAN<br></strong>",
        "_id": "2",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "A number of star golfers opted out of competing in Rio, with some saying Zika was their main deterrent. It now appears ",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://news.nationalpost.com/sports/rio-2016/zikas-olympic-zig-zag-the-search-for-a-balanced-message-between-fair-warning-and-unreasonable-fear\" target=\"_blank\">the threat of Zika was overstated </a>",
        "_id": "4",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc; but the golfers who did go to Rio should probably still think twice before throwing any and all caution to the wind.",
        "_id": "5",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Enter Henrik Stenson. As he walked down the fairway of the Olympic Golf Course during stroke play Saturday, the Swedish PGAer decided, for some reason, to reach into the water and ",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://www.golf.com/extra-spin/olympics-golf-henrik-stenson-plays-caiman-during-third-round\" target=\"_blank\">prod an caiman</a>",
        "_id": "7",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": " with a club. Fortunately for the golfer, the reptile didn&acirc;t stir. Stenson went on to earn the silver medal.",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<div id=\"fsk_splitbox_9\" class=\" fsk_splitbox_9\"></div>",
        "_id": "9",
        "type": "raw_html",
