        "content": "Shawn Barber keeps upping the ante. First, he won the 2015 NCAA championship, jumping for the University of Akron. Then he won the Pan American Games in his hometown, Toronto. And then he claimed gold at last year&acirc;s world championships. In Rio, his seasonal and personal best &acirc; six metres &acirc; is second among the 10 finalists, giving him a prime shot at yet another podium.",
