        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "A local sailing instructor is awaiting his sentence after pleading guilty to sexually abusing three 13-year-old boys between 2006 and 2009.",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Sean Hewson was escorted by family to the Burlington Courthouse Tuesday morning, where they sat across the courtroom from the 33-year-old&rsquo;s victims and their own supporters.",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Hewson &acirc; who initially faced 21 sexual assault-related charges after seven victims came forward to police &acirc; pleaded guilty in March to one count each of sexual exploitation by touching, sexual interference and invitation to sexual touching.",
        "_id": "5",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The Crown is seeking a sentence of three years. The defence wants 12 to 15 months. But it will be another two months before Justice David Harris delivers his decision and Hewson learns his fate.",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "As submissions wrapped up Tuesday, one of Hewson&rsquo;s victims &acirc; whose identities are protected by a publication ban &acirc; read out a victim impact statement, recalling the trauma of the abuse, which he kept secret for years.",
        "_id": "7",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;While my friends were having their first movie-date experiences with girlfriends and boyfriends, I was being groomed for a sexually abusive relationship that would span years of my life and impact my perception of what a healthy emotional and physical relationship should be forever,&rdquo; he said, his voice confident as he read.",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Back in 2006, he was 13. Hewson, then 23 or 24, was head instructor of the sailing program at the Burlington Sailing and Boating Club.",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "They became friends, according to the agreed statement of facts in the case, and Hewson would put him on his lap, eventually laying his hand on the boy&rsquo;s thighs.",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Over the next year, Hewson would take the boy to the clubhouse alone to watch movies. On one visit, he put his hand down the boy&rsquo;s pants and fondled him, then took the boy&rsquo;s hand and had him do the same thing.",
        "_id": "11",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Eventually this progressed to oral sex &acirc; which Hewson performed on the boy, and then had the boy perform on him &acirc; and culminated in Hewson performing anal sex on the boy.",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The sexual interference charge to which Hewson pleaded guilty stems from a 2009 relationship with a second 13-year-old boy whom he had been messaging on MSN chat after they met through mutual friends.",
        "_id": "13",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "In one instance, Hewson invited the boy to his house. He picked him up at a meeting spot and drove back to his New Street home, where he instructed the boy to pull down his pants. Hewson put him on his lap, fondling him. He then drove the boy home.",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "A few weeks later, Hewson again brought the boy to his house. They watched pornography and went to Hewson&rsquo;s bedroom, where, according to the agreed facts, he performed fellatio on the boy while masturbating.",
        "_id": "15",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The third charge &acirc; invitation to sexual touching &acirc; stemmed from a message Hewson sent to a boy over Facebook in summer 2006. According to the agreed facts, Hewson asked the 13-year-old boy to &ldquo;come over to his house and jerk him off.&rdquo;",
        "_id": "16",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "In his victim impact statement Tuesday, Hewson&rsquo;s victim spoke of his love of sailing &acirc; a joy that Hewson ruined for him, despite investing so much of his youth into the sport.",
        "_id": "17",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "He also spoke of his fears of running into Hewson now that he has finally started to heal. And he spoke of his frustrations with a slow-moving justice system, and the emotional toll it has taken on him.",
        "_id": "18",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;(My girlfriend) has witnessed my frustration at the countless delays, and the absurd liberties afforded to a man who is guilty, even by his own admission,&rdquo; he said.",
        "_id": "19",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&ldquo;The impact is that I no longer have confidence in the institutions of our society or in their aptitude for dealing with matters like this. I invite the court to address my mistrust when it gives its decision in this matter.&rdquo;",
        "_id": "20",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "When asked if he wanted to say anything Tuesday, Hewson, blankly, said &ldquo;no thank you.&rdquo;",
        "_id": "21",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "He will be back in court Oct. 14 to be sentenced.",
        "_id": "22",
