        "content": "<div> <p>Ontario Provincial Police have released the identities of two men killed in a fiery crash on Highway 2 outside of Brockville on Aug. 4.</p> <p>Scott Lockyer, 45, of Augusta Township was identified as the driver of the vehicle, while Adam Hrehirchuk, 22, of Winnipeg, was a passenger in the vehicle.</p> <p>The crash occurred at about 2 a.m., when a Volvo hatchbackÂ left the road at high speed,Â struckÂ a concrete post and landscape rock, then exploded in a fireball.</p> <p>Police said the investigation is continuing and asked anyone with information to call Prescott OPP at 613-925-4221.</p> </div>",
