    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/news/national/siu-investigates-after-man-critically-injured-in-confrontation-with-police/wcm/1eb31994-0309-4499-b9e2-21a06e677f69",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "SIU investigates after man critically injured in confrontation with police"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "content": "A 37-year-old man was in critical condition in hospital Sunday night after a police intervention that is being probed by ",
        "_id": "1",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"s1\">the </span>",
        "_id": "2",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Special Investigations Unit.",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The man was identified as Abdirahman Abdi by his sister, Hawa Abdi, who&Acirc;&nbsp;said she&Acirc;&nbsp;feared he would not recover",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"s1\">. He was being treated at The Ottawa Hospitalâs trauma centre.Â </span>",
        "_id": "5",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The SIU, the civilian&Acirc;&nbsp;oversight agency that&Acirc;&nbsp;investigates cases resulting in&Acirc;&nbsp;serious injuring, death or sexual assault&Acirc;&nbsp;",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"s1\">when police are involvedÂ said in a news releaseÂ </span>",
        "_id": "7",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "that&Acirc;&nbsp;a man attempting to elude arrest led police on a foot chase through Hintonburg in the Wellington Street West and Fairmont Avenue area around 10:30 a.m.",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The SIU&Acirc;&nbsp;said police confronted a&Acirc;&nbsp;man outside 55 Hilda St. and that &acirc;at some point during the confrontation, the man suffered medical distress.&acirc;",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "However, witnesses who spoke with&Acirc;&nbsp;",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "open",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"s1\">PostmediaÂ </span>",
        "_id": "11",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "said the man was beaten by multiple officers as he tried to run into an apartment building on Hilda Street. Witnesses said the man&Acirc;&nbsp;lay unconscious on the ground for about&Acirc;&nbsp;",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "none",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<span class=\"s1\">15 minutes before</span>",
        "_id": "13",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&Acirc;&nbsp;paramedics arrived&Acirc;&nbsp;and began administering CPR.",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "close",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;You can&acirc;t go against five cops at once,&acirc; said witness Asli Mohamed. &acirc;It was unnecessary.&acirc;",
        "_id": "15",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Mohamed, 20, a former resident of the apartment building, said she overheard police calling for backup before calling in paramedics.&Acirc;&nbsp;She said she saw blood &acirc;all over the place.&acirc;",
        "_id": "16",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;He looked weird &acirc; he looked dead,&acirc; she said. &acirc;It was weird that they didn&acirc;t (immediately) call paramedics.&Acirc;&nbsp;It took way too long. Everything was moving very slowly.&acirc;",
        "_id": "17",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      }
    ],
