    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "main": "Man found dead in Gatineau pool"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "content": "A coroner is investigating after a 32-year-old man was found dead in a swimming pool in Gatineau Tuesday morning.",
        "_id": "1",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Police and paramedics answered a 911 call at 9:43 a.m. about an unconscious man in the pool at a home on P.-Labine Street in the northeast part of the city. People at the scene were trying to revive the man when the officers&Acirc;&nbsp;arrived, but he was pronounced dead in hospital around noon.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "An investigation is under way, and although&Acirc;&nbsp;a coroner is involved police say there has been no decision on whether an autopsy is needed.",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "His name hasn&acirc;t been released.",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"mailto:tspears@postmedia.com\">tspears@postmedia.com</a>",
        "_id": "5",
        "type": "raw_html",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "<a href=\"http://twitter.com/TomSpears1\">twitter.com/TomSpears1</a>",
        "_id": "6",
