    "origin_url": "http://ottawacitizen.wpdev5.canada.com/news/local-news/test-story-2/wcm/9006545f-3fc2-41e1-9056-285e63d314ab",
    "status": "published",
    "titles": {
      "alternate": "Crime Story",
      "main": "test story"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "content": "A free man on borrowed time shot dead in Blossom Park. A young mother of two recovering in hospital. And a former friend and lover, suspected of killing one and trying to kill the other, on the run and out of sight.",
        "_id": "1",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Homicide detectives continued Wednesday to investigate the fatal shooting of Nicholas Kim, 30, the attempted murder of Katrina Galloway, 27, and to hunt wanted man Jonathan &acirc;Jonny&acirc; Ranger, 32, after a double shooting Tuesday night.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Police received a 911 call just after 9:30 p.m. Tuesday reporting the shooting on Farriers Lane in the city&acirc;s south end.",
        "_id": "3",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Neighbours said they heard the loud pops of what many assumed were fireworks leftover from the Victoria Day long weekend, what they estimated to be between four and five cracks into the night.",
        "_id": "4",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "A 20-year-old man said he had just returned to his townhouse on Farriers Lane after going for a run.",
        "_id": "5",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;I saw him lying on the ground, holding his chest,&acirc; said the young man. &acirc;She was screaming for help.&acirc;",
        "_id": "6",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The man, who asked that his name not be used, said he offered his shirt to another bystander to stanch the male victim&acirc;s&Acirc;&nbsp;wounds and ran to show police where to go when they arrived on scene. A police officer attempted CPR on the wounded man until paramedics arrived, he said.",
        "_id": "7",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;He was just like a rag doll when they picked him up,&acirc; the man said.",
        "_id": "8",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Both victims were taken to the trauma centre, where Kim was later pronounced dead.",
        "_id": "9",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Investigators have yet to determine the exact sequence of events but know that Ranger arrived at Galloway&acirc;s home at 2718 Farriers Ln. to find both her and Kim. Police have not yet determined the exact nature of the two victims&acirc; relationship but say there were, at the very least, friends, and had difficult relationships with the man accused of shooting them both.",
        "_id": "10",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Hours after Tuesday&acirc;s double shooting, police released Ranger&acirc;s mugshot. He is considered armed and dangerous and police urge anyone who may see him to call 9-1-1 immediately.",
        "_id": "11",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "In the last year, Ranger had been vocal about his strife with&Acirc;&nbsp;both Galloway and Kim.",
        "_id": "12",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Ranger and Galloway were former lovers who have a baby daughter together. Ranger recently grew angry at Galloway for what he claimed was her trying to keep their daughter from him, posting public rants alleging she was a bad mother and that children need their fathers. In his own words, he said he regretted not putting his hands on her, called her names and said she was manipulative. It hadn&acirc;t always been so caustic. In 2013, Galloway was proud of their relationship. In 2014, she and her son from a previous relationship, smiled happily in a group photo alongside Jonny&acirc;s family.",
        "_id": "13",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The now slain Kim and Ranger had also been friends. But, allegations began surfacing among gang circles that Kim had ratted on Ranger to police, creating a rift.",
        "_id": "14",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Kim, himself, was no stranger to shifting allegiances in the criminal world and was known throughout for his love of guns and drugs. In a 2014 trial, in which Ranger wasn&acirc;t involved, Kim was acquitted in a gangland shooting that saw a former partner-in-crime allege Kim shot a man in the legs in an east Ottawa park. The identity of that Crown witness, who called himself a &acirc;goof&acirc; and a &acirc;rat,&acirc; is shielded by a publication ban. But the court found he was liar who concocted a story.",
        "_id": "15",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "All three &acirc; Ranger, Galloway and Kim &acirc; are known to police.",
        "_id": "16",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Ranger and Galloway were charged together after a guns and gangs raid in Vanier in 2012. The former lovers were charged after a warrant turned up a 9-mm handgun, cocaine, oxycodone and marijuana. Galloway&acirc;s charges were later withdrawn.",
        "_id": "17",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Ranger was also convicted of kidnapping and extortion after he and two others jumped a man in stairwell in 2008, duct-taped his ankles and loaded him into a Cadillac. The man was beaten and robbed and Ranger was sent to jail.",
        "_id": "18",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "The alleged killer was also charged with fraud in 2006 for allegedly skimming credit cards at a gas station. He was convicted of assault in 2012 and has recent convictions for drug charges and dangerous driving in 2015.",
        "_id": "19",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Galloway was convicted of assault causing bodily harm in April 2013",
        "_id": "20",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Before his 2014 acquittal, Kim had a criminal record from a 2009 aggravated assault. Kim was convicted of drug possession in February of this year.",
        "_id": "21",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "After Kim&acirc;s 2014 acquittal, his lawyer Solomon Friedman said Kim had been &acirc;staring down the barrel of doing the better part of 10 years in prison.&acirc;",
        "_id": "22",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&acirc;He&acirc;s a free man now, taking life one day at a time.&acirc;",
        "_id": "23",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "Kim&acirc;s is the city&acirc;s 8th killing of the year, more than was seen in all of 2015 in Ottawa. His is the city&acirc;s 27th shooting of 2016.",
        "_id": "24",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "&nbsp;",
        "_id": "25",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
