    "titles": {
      "main": "Slicead Override Position Test"
    },
    "content_elements": [
      {
        "content": "Ten years ago a crack commando unit was sent to prison by a military court for a crime they didn&rsquo;t commit. These men promptly escaped from a maximum security stockade to the Los Angeles underground. Today, still wanted by the government, they survive as soldiers of fortune. If you have a problem and no one else can help, and if you can find them, maybe you can hire the A-team.",
        "_id": "1",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "content": "One for all and all for one, Muskehounds are always ready. One for all and all for one, helping everybody. One for all and all for one, it&rsquo;s a pretty story. Sharing everything with fun, that&rsquo;s the way to be. One for all and all for one, Muskehounds are always ready. One for all and all for one, helping everybody. One for all and all for one, can sound pretty corny. If you&rsquo;ve got a problem chum, think how it could be.",
        "_id": "2",
        "paragraph": "wrap",
        "type": "text",
        "channels": [
          "desktop",
          "tablet",
          "phone"
        ]
